{
  "texts": [
    "Batch size is set to 128.",
    "Typical data augmentations including random horizontal flip are applied.For Clothing-1M dataset, we follow the experimental setting in previous works [32].",
    "We use the 14k and 10k clean data for validation and test, respectively, and we do not use the 50k clean training data.",
    "We use ResNet-50 [3] pre-trained on ImageNet.",
    "For preprocessing, we resized the images to 256 × 256, performed mean subtraction, and cropped the middle 224 × 224."
  ]
}